         <abstract>
            <p>We report on a detailed study of the fundamental domain for the special linear group $\operatorname{SL}(3, \mathbf Z)$ of $3 \times 3$ integral matrices with determinant one. Graphs of points coming from the action of Hecke operators are considered.</p>
          </abstract>
